      "name": "Experimental validation of compression-bending QoIs required",
      "description": "The credibility plan mandates that all three quantities of interest (construct stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) be verified against physical bench-test measurements conducted under ASTM F1717 conditions. Verification must be performed through direct experimental comparison with hardware specimens.",
